但想法是，信托是法人实体，

991
00:59:01,530 --> 00:59:02,510
it's a legal thing.
这是合法的事情。

992
00:59:02,510 --> 00:59:04,070
It's kind of a company
这是一家公司

993
00:59:04,070 --> 00:59:07,650
but it's a different category of legal structure.
但这是法律结构的另一类。

994
00:59:07,650 --> 00:59:10,050
A trust is a
信任是一种

995
00:59:10,050 --> 00:59:13,830
kind of a holding vessel for funds that
是一种存放资金的船只

996
00:59:13,830 --> 00:59:19,030
a giver wants to give to beneficiaries but not immediately.
捐献者希望捐献给受益人，但不是马上就捐。

997
00:59:19,390 --> 00:59:21,010
